症），而且疫苗还减少了癌症的扩散，在某些情况下甚至完全阻止了癌症的扩散。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/nanoparticle-vaccine-prevents-multiple-cancers-and-stops-metastasis-in-mice.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Oct 2025 22:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/10/nanoparticle-vaccine-prevents-multiple-cancers-and-stops-metastasis-in-mice</guid></item></channel></rss>